          </div>
          <p class="lead"><%_i%>The tree is an hierarchical list of items related (and usually restricted) to a specific concept, which could be something like a content tree or a media tree.<%/i%></p>
          <p>The header of the tree contain a search function where you can easily access all content in Umbraco.</p> 
          <p>All icons in the tree are generated with a @font-face.</p>
          <p>The tree contains tree states. Normal, hover and active. In hover and active state it is posible to access the context menu. The context menu contain the ablity to create a new document and do something else.</p> 

